{"tid":2305159,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"余文樂定居台灣生活逍遙 閒來湊仔約彭于晏茶敍","createTime":"2020-11-29T11:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T05:27:04.000Z","uid":212249,"like":2,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"24ab8457e7fec125b58555e1651ffc48865a23fd","tid":2305159,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"余文樂與台灣「皮帶千金」王棠云於2017年結婚，2018年生下兒子後，他斥資約7400萬港元買入台北豪宅頂禾園的8000呎單位，為移居台灣做好準備，不經不覺他定居台北已經有年多，除了演藝事業，他在台灣有發展時裝生意。今年因疫情減少了工作量，他可以有較多時間留台陪老婆和兒子，而今日他就約了彭于晏茶敍。<br />\n<br />\n自從定居台灣後，他與彭于晏幾乎每周都相約見面，所以變得更加老友，而彭于晏很喜歡阿樂兒子Cody（余初見），所以有時約阿樂見面會要求帶埋Cody出來。余文樂在台北住了年幾後，已經好適應當地生活環境，在彭于晏幫助下，他已融入了台灣的演藝圈子，結識不少台灣藝人。"},{"pid":"e01220b4316f0cb4ddb81e6ddb781b69e5233a30","tid":2305159,"uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:48:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201129/3PKYEOH7DJDDDNTIBVHZ3BKHJE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201129%2F3PKYEOH7DJDDDNTIBVHZ3BKHJE%2F&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGieCCrfoqRshWq79J%2FX5JLMA%3D&h=a7af8f18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201129%2F3PKYEOH7DJDDDNTIBVHZ3BKHJE%2F&h=328804fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201129/3PKYEOH7DJDDDNTIBVHZ3BKHJE/</a>"},{"pid":"c5810ec03362d00b611700dc3a7b9a20762eefb8","tid":2305159,"uid":166405,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"做乜唔留係支那"},{"pid":"9e8b39df16829348c2de6f50fe21250ee1a24b37","tid":2305159,"uid":3405,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:56:15.000Z","msg":"2個支那人"},{"pid":"de03e6dcfae161c1592899ae787ae6a57dea3b3b","tid":2305159,"uid":278097,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:05:37.000Z","msg":"幹嗎要去台灣出賣祖國？"},{"pid":"3816d217763879ae6cca69306ae3be2ab386cfcf","tid":2305159,"uid":42396,"li